channel.title: -WishScape Reborn-
channel.description:
Well some of you may know WishScape From like 2008. It was based of czar. Probly was the best czar server in those days. It holded 120+ with no lagg or crash. Well I quited and shut down the server. Now im back and working on a new project. The base is Devolution 2.6. [b]NOTE: Do not pm and ask can I help you code it. I don't accept and invites. Im doing this solo so it wont fail like most projects do. Some get relased and some just die.[/b] Ok so my youtube account is Youtube.com/WishScape I will be posting my progress there. Here are some futures.
[font=Verdana][size=10pt][u]Futures[/u][/size][/font] -Fully Working Npc/Player Dialouge talking. -100% Fully Working Woodcutting. With Tree's Falling and getting logs with correct timers in each tree. -Current working skills. That are made from scratch. Woodcutting,Smithing,Mining. Will be showing in vid. -Perfect Attack Delays. And Correct Npc Facing In combat. -Working on PVP -No Quest. Don't have quest system yet. Will get soon -4 Fully working towns. Such as Faldor,Varrock,Lumby, and Ardougne. -All trees are used all over the world -Unlike other servers this server you will be able to play through the whole world with over 20 quest's -Minigames: NONE -Special attacks: Crap -Low CPU Usage. -----------------------------
Will be posting updates in an hour or 2
